{"tid":141932,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓啲屎成日都好軟","createTime":"2017-03-03T10:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T04:39:24.000Z","uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05d0d63a21116f71b600a8aaabbcac3c022ce2e1","tid":141932,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"一歲貓 之前餵wellness core <br />\n啲屎一直都有啲軟 但都仲係條狀 唔係爛屎<br />\n上網睇可能wellness 太多蛋白質<br />\n就幫佢轉左fromm <br />\n但都係冇咩改善<br />\n有試過蒸雞柳比佢 好少少<br />\n同埋有時見到d 屎會有d 血既黏液咁 但唔係成日<br />\n有餵杜蟲藥 平時好精神玩得訓得咩事都冇<br />\n洗唔洗睇醫生？ 如果睇醫院係咪都係驗大便？<br />\n有冇d 咩可以做？"},{"pid":"ca968bdda7cc63e904720100e4c1beaafbfd9c22","tid":141932,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"Wellness core邊款<br />\n我都驚隻貓軟便，揀左隻低少少蛋白質<br />\n粉紅色包裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195105_2cf42672b162c9eb4c80aa32723cbb9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195105_2cf42672b162c9eb4c80aa32723cbb9f.jpg&h=0f2c5150&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTmQJyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTmQJyk.jpg&h=08bc6cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"830f9e7f8c117bd5f1c49b4083373c863f9c41ef","tid":141932,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Wellness core邊款<br />\n我都驚隻貓軟便，揀左隻低少少蛋白質<br />\n粉紅色包裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195105_2cf42672b162c9eb4c80aa32723cbb9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195105_2cf42672b162c9eb4c80aa32723cbb9f.jpg&h=0f2c5150&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTmQJyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTmQJyk.jpg&h=08bc6cf3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係買火雞 原味個隻"},{"pid":"232f6a9f2d1b9041cbdfc609180225500a064262","tid":141932,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"剩係試過呢兩隻糧？<br />\n係咪餵得多過每日需要？如果係就要跟番份量餵<br />\n試下有無改善<br />\n<br />\n跟足份量都軟便先有機會對某樣食物敏感<br />\n外國獸醫有得check動物對咩敏感，唔知香港有無<br />\n唔係就要續隻糧試"},{"pid":"8019ba91abd3d02652c46f8a4999ba69d2d46996","tid":141932,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"爭好唔好食"},{"pid":"30e4edce05a18ea0d7c90261d1d6b7e23ad6fff5","tid":141932,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剩係試過呢兩隻糧？<br />\n係咪餵得多過每日需要？如果係就要跟番份量餵<br />\n試下有無改善<br />\n<br />\n跟足份量都軟便先有機會對某樣食物敏感<br />\n外國獸醫有得check動物對咩敏感，唔知香港有無<br />\n唔係就要續隻糧試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦～咁有可能喎<br />\n平時真係冇跟分量比 <br />\n試下先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該哂絲打！"},{"pid":"1099732f80d99ac3a277700179c08aacbaee7548","tid":141932,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剩係試過呢兩隻糧？<br />\n係咪餵得多過每日需要？如果係就要跟番份量餵<br />\n試下有無改善<br />\n<br />\n跟足份量都軟便先有機會對某樣食物敏感<br />\n外國獸醫有得check動物對咩敏感，唔知香港有無<br />\n唔係就要續隻糧試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦～咁有可能喎<br />\n平時真係冇跟分量比 <br />\n試下先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該哂絲打！</blockquote><br />\n尤其高蛋白糧因爲營養足，餵太多吸收唔晒，<br />\n減少份量隻貓可能唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得唔飽<br />\n試下其中一餐轉罐，易飽啲同吸收多啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}